WEBVTT

00:09:30.136 --> 00:09:31.335
To achieve that,

00:09:31.359 --> 00:09:36.258
the local agriculture is increasing
its focus on date palms and grapevines.

00:09:37.077 --> 00:09:40.577
Those two are much more tolerant
to drought conditions

00:09:40.601 --> 00:09:42.452
than many other fruits and vegetables,

00:09:42.941 --> 00:09:44.528
and at the same time,

00:09:44.552 --> 00:09:49.719
they are considered high-value crops,
both locally and internationally.

00:09:50.711 --> 00:09:52.271
Locals in Namibia,

00:09:53.073 --> 00:09:56.561
one of the most arid countries
in Southern Africa,

00:09:56.585 --> 00:10:00.984
have been drinking
recycled water since 1968.